Gina said to be here at 6:30.
translation.fr: Gina a dit d'être là à 6h30.

translation.en: Where is she?
Maybe she overslept?
You wanna know why that just happened? Because you weren't ready!
translation.fr: Tu sais pourquoi c'est arrivé ? Tu n'étais pas prêt !

translation.en: All the teams we're about to face this week have one thing in common.
translation.fr: Toutes les équipes ont un point commun.

translation.en: They were actually chosen to compete?
Well, yeah.
-They've been training for months? -Yeah, that too.
They're the pride of their countries, and we're a bunch of underdogs nobody believes in?
translation.fr: Leur pays est fier d'elles mais personne ne croit en nous ?

translation.en: I was gonna say they're ready for anything.
translation.fr: J'allais dire qu'elles sont prêtes à tout.

translation.en: The Beachmaster is a grueling obstacle course
translation.fr: Le Grand Prix est une course d'obstacles

translation.en: designed to put lifeguarding's most important skills to the test:
translation.fr: conçue pour tester l'habileté des sauveteurs :

translation.en: strength, endurance, agility, and, most importantly, teamwork.
translation.fr: la force, l'endurance, l'agilité, et, surtout, le travail d'équipe.

translation.en: The team that gets through the course the fastest, wins.
The whole team.
That means we have to work together.
No problem. We're Tower Two. Teamwork is our jam.
translation.fr: Nickel. Le travail d'équipe ? On gère.

translation.en: Good. Then this should be easy.
Now move your butts! We've got work to do!
-[whistle blares] -[Lizzie] Ooh! Oh, sorry!
-[Tyler] Let's go! -[Gina] Really?
[Dylan] Let's move away from here. Head that way. Okay.
Yeah, come on! Let's go, Dylan!
Whoo! Come on! You got this! Move those legs! Let's go! Yeah!
translation.fr: Tu vas y arriver ! Bouge tes jambes ! Ouais !

translation.en: After you.
-Eric, what are you doing? -Holding the wire for my lady.
translation.fr: - Tu fais quoi ? - Je laisse passer la dame.

translation.en: Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't know you two were out on a date.
translation.fr: Oh, désolée, vous êtes en rendez-vous ?

translation.en: I thought we were training for the most important competition of our lives!
translation.fr: On ne s'entraîne pas pour la course de notre vie ?

translation.en: -Move it! Move it! -[whistle blares]
Let's go! Come on!
Keep it up! Let's go!
Go! Whoo!
-[Tyler] Oh, come on, guys! -[Lizzie] I got it! I got it!
Come on, guys! Teamwork makes the dream work!
Let's go, you maggots! Go! Go! Go!
Come on! Go, slowpoke!
Come on, Eric! Let's go! Let's go! You've got this! Come on! Let's move it!
translation.fr: Allez, Eric ! C'est parti ! C'est bon ! On se bouge !

translation.en: -[Tyler] You got this, Dylan. -[Gina] Good job, Tyler! Come on! Come on!
translation.fr: - Tu gères, Dylan. - Bien joué, Tyler. Allez !

translation.en: I got you.
-More training, less flirting! -Uh...
-Sick teamwork, bro. -Nice save, dog!
Oops! Sorry!
All you have to do is get across this line.
translation.fr: Vous devez juste passer cette ligne.

translation.en: -That's it? -[Gina] Yep.
This feels like a trap.
If it's a trap, don't worry. I'll protect you.
translation.fr: Ne t'inquiète pas, je te protège.

translation.en: I can protect myself.
Guys, it's not a trap!
Then why am I holding a riot shield?
translation.fr: Alors, pourquoi je tiens un bouclier ?

translation.en: Because it is a trap!
Everybody get behind me!
[Lizzie] Come on, Dylan! A couple of more steps! Come on!
Now push! We're almost there!
That's it! Great teamwork!
translation.fr: Ça y est ! Super travail d'équipe !

translation.en: -[Dylan] God. -[Lizzie] Push! You got it!
Push!
I told you to be prepared for anything!
translation.fr: Je vous ai dit d'être prêts à tout !

translation.en: You guys, help me with this thing!
[Tyler] We gotta grab it! Okay.
[Dylan] I can't get it.
You guys distract it, and I'll sneak up behind it!
You can't distract it! It's a hose, you moron!
translation.fr: On ne peut pas, c'est un tuyau, abruti !

translation.en: [Dylan] A little this way.
-[Lizzie] Hey! -[Tyler] A little closer.
[Dylan] I can't.
-Grab it! Somebody grab it! -[Gina] I got it! I got it!
Don't worry. I got it.
Hey, settle down, sunshine.
This is a job for a big fella, not a little wallaby like you.
translation.fr: Laisse faire les grands garçons, petit wallaby.

translation.en: We did it!
Yes! We killed it!
Uh, guys?
Everybody okay?
Yeah, we're just doing a little training.
Ah. Sorry.
Do you, uh, want me to turn it back on, do ya?
[all] No!
Look, we're kind of wrapping it up, anyway.
translation.fr: On a terminé, de toute façon.

translation.en: -You guys all right? -Depends. How much of that did you see?
translation.fr: - Ça va ? - Ça dépend. Tu as vu quoi ?

translation.en: All of it, mate.
Well, then, we've been better. I'm Eric!
translation.fr: On a connu mieux. Je m'appelle Eric !

translation.en: Oh! I'm Kezza.
And that's Johnno, Shaz, Carli, and that's Wayno.
translation.fr: Voici Johnno, Shaz, Carli, et Wayno.

translation.en: So, you guys are the new Team USA?
translation.fr: Vous êtes la nouvelle équipe USA ?

translation.en: Looks like we got some stiff competition, boys?
Don't worry. We'll be ready by Friday.
Oh, of course you will be.
You guys are doing a ripper job out there, right, Wayno?
translation.fr: Vous faites du super boulot, pas vrai ?

translation.en: Yeah, sure.
Just messing with you, mate.
Hey...
you forgot your wrench.
Yeah, it must have been cracked or something.
You guys are in trouble.
Would you get out of here?
Oh, she's right. We are in trouble.
translation.fr: Elle a raison. On est mal barrés.

translation.en: He's been going nonstop for three days. [chuckles] Oh, gosh. Eh!
translation.fr: Il ne s'est pas arrêté depuis trois jours. Oh, mon Dieu.

translation.en: Everyone stay on this side of his canvas.
translation.fr: Tout le monde reste de ce côté de la toile.

translation.en: Do not interrupt him.
Come on! Pick it up!
Eric, what are you doing?
-Keeping you company. -You don't have to.
translation.fr: - Je t'attends. - Tu n'es pas obligé.

translation.en: I know. I want to.
translation.fr: Je sais, mais j'en ai envie.

translation.en: Let's go!
Morning, brother.
Going for a little walkey-walkey, are we?
Wish I didn't see that.
translation.fr: J'aurais préféré ne pas voir ça.

translation.en: I can dig some holes where the other teams will be running.
translation.fr: Je creuse des trous là où courent les autres ?

translation.en: A few broken ankles would really even the odds.
translation.fr: Des chevilles cassées égaliseraient les chances.

translation.en: That's sweet, honey, but I think it'd be best if you just stayed out of the way.
translation.fr: C'est gentil, chérie, mais tu devrais rester à l'écart.

translation.en: Nobody will let me do anything.
Why do you keep making me come to Junior Rescue?
Oh, don't worry.
If things keep going the way they're going,
there won't be a Junior Rescue to come back to.
[woman shouts] Jeffy!
Where are you?
You seen my great big meatball sandwich?
translation.fr: Tu as vu mon sandwich aux boulettes ?

translation.en: -[woman] Jeffy! -[record scratches, music stops]
Where are you?
[Gina] Listen up!
The trick with the cargo net is to move opposing limbs in unison
translation.fr: Pour le filet, bougez les membres opposés à l'unisson

translation.en: and stick as close as you can to the support beams.
Lizzie, you're up first.
And try not to make me puke.
Come on, Lizzie, move it! Move it!
-[Lizzie grunts] -Uh, I-- I got you!
No, Eric! Let her do it!
-[grunts] I had it! -I know.
-Then why did you come up here? -I-- I just want to be here for you.
translation.fr: - Alors pourquoi t'es venu  ? - Pour t'aider.

translation.en: Tyler, Dylan. Get in there and show 'em how it's done.
-Like together? -We're not together.
-I know that. -What's going on with you two?
translation.fr: - Je sais. - C'est quoi le problème ?

translation.en: Nothing, let's just go.
[Lizzie] Ow! Oh! A lot of movement over there. Ow!
Okay! Okay!
That's Tyler's leg.
Who put this thing--
Ah! Getting a little light-headed!
This went wrong so fast.
translation.fr: Ça a très vite mal tourné.

translation.en: [woman] Help!
Hey! Somebody needs our help!
-[woman] Help! -[man] Hey!
-[man] Come on! -[woman] Hey!
We're on it!
-Gina, a little help here? -We have to save them! Come on!
translation.fr: - Gina, tu m'aides ? - On doit les sauver !

translation.en: [Wayno] Aussies on this one.
Johnno and Carli, you take the one on the left!
translation.fr: Johnno et Carli, celui de gauche !

translation.en: [Kezza] All right, let's go. Now. Shaz and Johnno, in the water now.
translation.fr: Allez, on y va. Shaz et Johnno, dans l'eau.

translation.en: [Wayno] Let's go. Come on, team. You got it.
Watch out for the rips.
[Wayno] Let's go, team. Come on.
translation.fr: On y va, les gars. Allez.

translation.en: Hey! I said we're on it.
[Wayno] Let's go, team. Come on.
Let's go. You're doing' great. Bring 'em in.
Okay, bring 'em up. Come on.
[Tyler] Come on!
All right, yeah. That was amazing, Shaz. Good work.
-Good stuff, team. -That was amazing.
Is everybody okay?
Oh, yeah. No worries, mate.
We just saw that youse were a bit busy with your net over there,
translation.fr: On a vu que vous étiez occupés avec le filet,

translation.en: so we jumped in.
We didn't mean to show you up or nothing.
translation.fr: On n'a pas voulu vous humilier.

translation.en: -You didn't show us up. -Oh, you reckon, do ya?
translation.fr: - C'est pas le cas. - Tu crois ?

translation.en: We're the ones who saved those shark biscuits
translation.fr: On les a sauvés des requins,

translation.en: while you were flopping around like a mudskipper going walkabout.
translation.fr: alors que vous étiez perdus dans le bush.

translation.en: I can't tell. Are you guys nice people, or are you not nice people?
translation.fr: Je n'arrive pas à savoir si vous êtes gentils ou pas ?

translation.en: Yeah, I thought we kind of bonded over the whole "Brody's a drongo" thing.
translation.fr: Je croyais que ce drongo de Brody nous avait rapprochés.

translation.en: Yeah, look, that's when he was the drongo.
translation.fr: Oui, quand c'était lui le drongo.

translation.en: Now you're the drongo, drongo.
I'm coming down on "not nice."
We came here... with one mission...
translation.fr: On est venus ici avec une mission :

translation.en: To destroy Team USA.
I just didn't think it was gonna be this easy, eh?
translation.fr: Ça va être plus facile que prévu.

translation.en: Good bit of luck with the real team getting sick like that?
I know what the problem is.
translation.fr: Je sais quel est le problème.

translation.en: I've been way too easy on you!
translation.fr: J'ai été trop sympa avec vous !

translation.en: I wouldn't say that.
Tomorrow, I drop the hammer!
Don't worry. We'll get through this together.
Oh, what? 'Cause I can't do it by myself?
translation.fr: Car je ne peux pas le faire toute seule ?

translation.en: I didn't mean...
Man, none of this would be happening if Brody and his team hadn't gotten sick.
translation.fr: On n'en serait pas là si l'équipe USA n'était pas malade.

translation.en: Okay, well, they did, okay?
I don't know why you're yelling at me about it!
I didn't mean...
What's wrong with Tyler?
How would I know?
It's not like I sit around thinking about Tyler all the time!
translation.fr: Je ne pense pas à lui tout le temps !

translation.en: My head's in the game! [grunts]
I didn't mean...
Actually, I don't know what I meant.
translation.fr: Je ne sais pas ce que je voulais dire.

translation.en: Ho! Excuse me.
I didn't realize there was anyone else in the building.
I, too, do my best work after hours.
translation.fr: Moi aussi, je travaille mieux le soir.

translation.en: I'm in a band.
If you don't mind, I'll give you one of my CDs.
translation.fr: Si tu veux bien, je te donne un de mes disques.

translation.en: You could listen to it,
maybe give me a little feedback, one artist to another.
translation.fr: et dis-moi ce que tu en penses, d'artiste à artiste.

translation.en: I've got my, uh, e-mail on the back,
translation.fr: J'ai mis mon e-mail au dos,

translation.en: and my Twitter handle. Or you could just hit me up on LinkedIn.
translation.fr: et mon pseudo Twitter. Ou tu peux me contacter sur LinkedIn.

translation.en: I'd love to make you part of my network.
I'll just leave this here.
I really like that guy.
Quiet, good listener.
Right.
How ya doing, Gina?
If you're here to trash-talk my team, don't. I'm not in the mood.
translation.fr: Si t'es là pour nous descendre, arrête. Je ne suis pas d'humeur.

translation.en: Oh, no, I'm not here to trash-talk your team.
translation.fr: Oh non, je ne suis pas là pour ça.

translation.en: We're all Junior Rescue. We gotta stick together.
translation.fr: On doit se serrer les coudes.

translation.en: It doesn't matter where we come from.
I'm actually here to give you a little pep talk.
And why would you do that?
Um, because if you go into competition as bad as you are,
translation.fr: Parce que si vous êtes aussi mauvais lors du tournoi,

translation.en: we're gonna look like huge jerks when we kick your bums.
translation.fr: on aura l'air de gros crétins sans pitié.

translation.en: People will be like, "Oh, why'd you humiliate those Yanks?"
We'll be like, "We didn't mean to. It's not our fault they're incompetent."
translation.fr: On dira : "On n'y peut rien s'ils sont incompétents."

translation.en: They'll be like, "Too right. They're a bunch of bogans."
And I'll be like, "Hey, hey, hey. Lay off 'em, cause those bogans are our mates."
translation.fr: On dira : "Hé ! Lâchez-les, ces culs-terreux sont nos potes."

translation.en: We've just had a couple off days. We're gonna win this thing.
translation.fr: On a eu un passage à vide. On va gagner.

translation.en: Oh, yes. See, look, that's the spirit.
And don't even worry about the fact that you're representing your entire country
translation.fr: Ne stressez pas en pensant que vous représentez votre pays

translation.en: or that tomorrow you're gonna completely humiliate yourself
translation.fr: ou que vous allez vous humilier devant le monde entier.

translation.en: -in front of the world. -You're trying to get in my head.
translation.fr: ou que vous allez vous humilier devant le monde entier. Tu veux me faire peur.

translation.en: Oh, no, I'm not trying to get in your head. [laughs]
I'm already in there.
And you? [laughs] You don't stand a chance.
translation.fr: Et vous ? Vous n'avez aucune chance.

translation.en: Catch you later.
Is it me, or is she even scarier when she's not yelling?
translation.fr: C'est plus flippant quand elle ne crie pas, non ?

translation.en: She's "Mom mad." That's the maddest you can be.
translation.fr: On dirait une mère furieuse, ça craint.

translation.en: Do you want to lose tomorrow?
Speaking for me and Lizzie?
-No. -Eric, I can speak for myself.
translation.fr: - Non. - Je peux parler pour moi.

translation.en: -No. -'Cause it feels like you wanna lose.
translation.fr: - Non. - On dirait que vous voulez perdre.

translation.en: I've been racking my brain trying to figure out how you could possibly be this bad,
translation.fr: Je me creuse la tête pour comprendre comment vous pouvez être aussi nuls,

translation.en: and all I could come up with is that you hate Junior Rescue.
translation.fr: et j'en conclus que vous détestez le programme.

translation.en: Well, you need to reexamine your conclusions, because we love Junior Rescue.
translation.fr: C'est faux. On adore les Sauveteurs Juniors.

translation.en: Well, you're not training like you love it.
You're training like a bunch of bogans.
What's a bogan?
It's what you're training like!
You're distracted, and your teamwork sucks.
translation.fr: Vous êtes distraits, votre travail d'équipe pue.

translation.en: We've got one more day to get ready. But you have to want it.
translation.fr: Il nous reste un jour de préparation. Mais il faut le vouloir.

translation.en: All of you. Do you want to win?
Of course we do.
Then what's the problem?
They're way better than us.
You're trying to steal our secrets, are ya?
I mean, you can if you want.
You still don't have a prayer. Ha ha!
You see that?
That thing I just did.
That was sweet as, right?
Let's see what you got, Team Drongo.
translation.fr: À vous de jouer, Équipe Drongo.

translation.en: -That was awesome, mate. So sick. -That was good, right?
translation.fr: - C'était ouf, trop cool. - Pas mal, hein ?

translation.en: [sighs] Four days isn't enough time.
translation.fr: Quatre jours, ça ne suffit pas.

translation.en: I thought I could get us ready, but I was wrong.
translation.fr: Je pensais que j'y arriverais, mais j'avais tort.

translation.en: I'm sorry I let you down.
No, we let you down.
Yeah. We could have trained harder.
translation.fr: Oui. On aurait pu s'entraîner plus.

translation.en: I mean, every time I try to sit, I go, "Ow."
translation.fr: Chaque fois que je m'assieds, je dis "aïe".

translation.en: I think I could've given a little more.
Gina, we weren't even supposed to be doing this.
translation.fr: On n'était même pas censés participer.

translation.en: If Brody and the guys hadn't got sick--
Okay, fine! It's my fault! Is that what you wanted me to say?
translation.fr: OK. C'est ma faute ! C'est ce que vous voulez ?

translation.en: Dude, what did you do?
Brody was strutting around at the barbecue bragging that he was Team USA,
translation.fr: Au barbecue, Brody se vantait d'être l'équipe USA,

translation.en: and we weren't. So I pulled a prank on him.
translation.fr: donc je lui ai fait une blague.

translation.en: I gave him that rotten coleslaw.
translation.fr: Je lui ai servi le chou pourri.

translation.en: Tyler, why would you do that?
translation.fr: Pourquoi tu ferais un truc pareil ?

translation.en: I didn't know everybody else was gonna eat it. And I definitely didn't know they were gonna get sick.
translation.fr: J'ignorais que les autres en mangeraient, et qu'ils tomberaient malades.

translation.en: That coleslaw was 17 years old, man.
translation.fr: Cette salade de chou avait 17 ans.

translation.en: What'd you think was gonna happen?
I wasn't thinking, okay?
This whole year I was so excited to come back to Junior Rescue.
translation.fr: Toute l'année, j'ai rêvé des Sauveteurs Juniors.

translation.en: Now there might not even be a Junior Rescue.
Because of me.
Where do you think you're going, soldier? Hey, you get back here!
translation.fr: Tu penses aller où, soldat ? Hé, reviens ici !

translation.en: That's an order!
[sighs] Can you believe him?
I bet we would have had a shot at this thing if the Aussies hadn't gotten in our heads.
translation.fr: Sans les Australiens, on aurait une chance.

translation.en: I wish they would get food poisoning.
I don't actually mean that. I'm just having a lot of feelings now.
translation.fr: Je ne le pensais pas. Ça fait trop d'émotions pour moi.

translation.en: Give it a rest, kid.
[woman] Jeffy! You seen my radio?
translation.fr: Jeffy ! Tu as vu ma radio ?

translation.en: -[music clicks off] -[woman] Jeffy!
Hey! Get back here! What are you-- Ow! Ow!
God! Stubbed my big toe on this giant heart made out of rocks!
translation.fr: Bon sang ! Je me suis cogné l'orteil sur ce cœur géant en pierres !

translation.en: Jeffy, did you put this here? Is this you?
translation.fr: Jeffy, c'est toi qui as fait ça ? C'est toi ?

translation.en: Hey, get back here! Jeffy!
[Brody] Mom!
I'm all out of juice!
Mom!
Hey, you're not my mom!
translation.fr: Hé, tu n'es pas ma mère !

translation.en: What are you doing in my room?
Just wanted to stop by, see how you're doing.
translation.fr: Je voulais voir comment tu allais.

translation.en: My tummy's still a little bit rumbly, but... I guess I feel a bit better.
translation.fr: Mon ventre gargouille toujours un peu, mais je me sens un peu mieux.

translation.en: Well, that's great. That's great news.
You and the team can still get out and win this thing. Come on, man.
translation.fr: Vous pouvez encore gagner. Allez, mec.

translation.en: What are you, crazy?
I haven't eaten solid food in four days. I can't stand up without getting dizzy,
translation.fr: J'ai rien mangé depuis quatre jours. Debout, j'ai des vertiges,

translation.en: and my doctor says I have the butthole of a 65-year-old man!
translation.fr: et mon docteur dit que j'ai le cul d'un mec de 65 ans !

translation.en: Look, there's something I gotta tell you.
translation.fr: Il faut que je te dise un truc.

translation.en: I knew that coleslaw was expired.
translation.fr: Je savais que le chou était périmé.

translation.en: But for the record, you were supposed to spit it out.
translation.fr: Mais tu étais censé le recracher.

translation.en: This is...
awesome. [laughs]
-You're not mad? -Oh, no, I'm furious.
translation.fr: - Tu ne m'en veux pas ? - Je suis furieux.

translation.en: I was supposed to make history this year.
This whole time, I have been thinking I let everyone down.
translation.fr: Tout ce temps, je pensais que c'était ma faute.

translation.en: But you let everyone down!
Trust me. I feel worse about it than you do.
translation.fr: Je me sens plus mal que toi.

translation.en: Oh, I guarantee you that is not true.
You were right, man. I'm not Team USA material.
translation.fr: Tu avais raison. Je ne suis pas au niveau.

translation.en: -Duh. -We can't do this. We can't win it.
Oh, boo-hoo-hoo! Look at me. I'm Tyler. I'm a big crybaby.
translation.fr: Je m'appelle Tyler. Je suis un gros pleurnicheur.

translation.en: You wanna know why you're so annoying?
Not really.
It's because you never give up.
Oh, my God, it drives me crazy. It is by far your worst quality.
translation.fr: Ça me rend dingue. C'est de loin ta pire qualité.

translation.en: -Uh, thanks? -So why are you giving up now?
The Beachmaster is tomorrow.
You screwed this up.
You need to fix it. You should be out there kicking butt,
translation.fr: Tu dois régler ça. Tu devrais te démener,

translation.en: but you're in my bedroom crying like a giant wuss.
translation.fr: mais t'es ici à chialer comme une mauviette.

translation.en: That's not the Tyler I know and hate.
translation.fr: Ce n'est pas le Tyler que je hais.

translation.en: So you're saying I felt so bad about what I did I lost my edge?
translation.fr: Tu dis que j'étais aussi nul parce que je m'en voulais ?

translation.en: -I don't remember saying that. -You mean mistakes are in the past.
translation.fr: Je n'ai pas dit ça. Et qu'il faut oublier le passé et faire mieux à l'avenir ?

translation.en: Best way to make it right is do better in the future?
translation.fr: Et qu'il faut oublier le passé et faire mieux à l'avenir ?

translation.en: What you talking about?
translation.fr: - De quoi tu parles ? - Tu as raison.

translation.en: You're right, man! Look, I can't give up!
translation.fr: - De quoi tu parles ? - Tu as raison. Je ne peux pas abandonner. Je vous le dois à tous.

translation.en: I owe it to you and my team and all of Junior Rescue to fix this.
translation.fr: Je ne peux pas abandonner. Je vous le dois à tous.

translation.en: Well, yeah, that's true, but--
This is huge, Brody!
-Thanks, man. -Oh! Get off me.
You better not tell anybody I inspired you!
translation.fr: Ne dis à personne que je t'ai motivé !

translation.en: Hug was kinda nice, though.
Of all the days for your brother to be late, it had to be today.
translation.fr: Comment ton frère peut-il être en retard aujourd'hui ?

translation.en: So irresponsible.
I cannot believe it-- Gah!
Took you long enough.
Please promise me you're gonna win this thing today.
I'll promise you this: we're not gonna give up.
translation.fr: Je te promets qu'on n'abandonnera pas.

translation.en: That is not what I asked you to promise me.
translation.fr: Ce n'est pas ce que je t'ai demandé.

translation.en: What are you smirking about back there?
Just got a feeling that today might work out.
translation.fr: Je sens que ça va bien se passer.

translation.en: Aw! You got faith in your big bro?
translation.fr: Tu crois en ton grand frère ?

translation.en: Ew. No, gross.
Hey, Lizzie!
Does Eric have a goldfish?
'Cause, uh, he's acting like it died.
translation.fr: On dirait qu'il vient de mourir.

translation.en: I'm sorry I've been so snappy lately.
